WEBVTT

00:00:16.726 --> 00:00:18.066
Zamislite ovo:

00:00:18.066 --> 00:00:20.391
ti i tvoj prijatelj gledate humorističnu seriju

00:00:20.391 --> 00:00:22.765
i vrckavi sporedni lik ušeta u sobu,

00:00:22.765 --> 00:00:25.011
noseći svadbenu tortu na četiri kata.

00:00:25.011 --> 00:00:25.949
Saplete se,

00:00:25.949 --> 00:00:26.540
padne,

00:00:26.540 --> 00:00:28.672
i zabije se licem ravno u tortu.

